Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:07.25,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,96)\pos(348,346)}Reichwein Counseling Center \N (Munich)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.58,0:00:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had any liquor since?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you stay away from the stuff, \N you can turn over a new leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been unable to drink since I \N started seeing you each week...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared to death of your angry thunderstorms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, my thunderstorms?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only counseling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't have time to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got my first big case since \N switching to being a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big case?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, what do you think of this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your skill at physiognomy, can \N you tell me what kind of man he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Physiognomy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.40,0:00:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm a psychic or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are known for being able to tell what \N someone is like just by looking at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only good at that because of my \N many years of counseling people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then with your skill, could you tell me if he's a fraud?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fraud?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!  This one's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's unable to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he tried, he'd be easily exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How likely is he to commit suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have the face of one who would commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you sound so confident, I'm convinced \N of your skills at physiognomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just because of my years of experience at counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is something wrong with that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.56,0:01:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hans Georg Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, you know of him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the billionaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Vampire of Bayern.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.  That billionaire hired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:02:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man in this photo, Edmund \N Fahren, claimed to be his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!  His lies were quickly exposed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Schuwald completely believed his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite a setup.  It took me a while \N to discover that he was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still don't understand something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was he so well acquainted with Schuwald's son's \N background that Schuwald actually believed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you ask him about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, he has already committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:06.05,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,75)\pos(359,340)}The Secret Forest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it go, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, for old times' sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see Edmund Fahren's suicide note.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The handwriting analysis has already been done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it, that was his handwriting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason to show it to an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first two witnesses, Karl Neumann and Lotte Frank...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They worked with Fahren, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just friends, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how are you guys doing?  Same as always?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we never have enough manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since taking over your job, I've barely had any free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dull-witted Martin has gotten high and mighty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever call me that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are no longer my boss, and I'm \N no longer your subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, Martin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem to understand how hard it was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We spent so much time tracking that serial killer, and \N just when we were about to make the arrest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you shot him in your drunken stupor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't believe how much trouble \N it was, cleaning up your mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you will excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to deal with such a simple suicide case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to check out the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is still intact, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since it's not really a crime scene, I've already \N given permission to clean the place up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they are moving the victim's belongings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did dull-witted Martin get so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, I'm in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movers will be coming to pick \N everything up soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll just be a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hung a rope from the pipe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wrote his suicide note on this desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was writing a paper on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Birth of Tragedy," "Process and Reality," \N "The Sense of the World."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely the bookshelf of a philosophy student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the source material for \N the essay he was working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?  Oh, this is "The Gallic War."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This book is unrelated to the others, so why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spanish?  No, Latin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a clue what language this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a new book, but why is this \N the only underlined passage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room 204... Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we need more boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Load up the books first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great job, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you some questions about your neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already told you people everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm not a cop.  I'm a private investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a paper due tomorrow, but thanks \N to all the commotion next door...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I haven't been able to concentrate at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, just one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were these two people close to Fahren?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I've never seen them here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't seem to have many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, just one more question...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can translate this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the underlined passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be your fault if I fail my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...deceive..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?  That's good enough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...deceive..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have I heard this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like this spot too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you are... Johan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get a much better view up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said stop!  It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the lights coming on in \N all the houses around this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Families come home...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of dinner is in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You envy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I haven't had anything like that since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was your family like?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guess that is a touchy subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I've been in foster homes since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, would you tell me about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!  This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't deceive him anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fahren's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, those weren't his last words...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was only translating the line from that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the story of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda depressing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm talking to you, I feel like I can say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you said just now, about your rich father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are talking about Schuwald, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan, you are crying... for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we have to do something about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:12:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but worry about Schuwald, \N since I'm taking care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Fahren's suicide, he hasn't been eating much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes on, he might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl, why don't you tell him you are his real son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to know what kind of person he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell him the truth, he would probably \N think I'm only after his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Schuwald is like.  Everything is \N about money to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your own father is wallowing in despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that is what is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is the case, I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't deceive him anymore..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those weren't Fahren's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found this Latin book in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He simply translated this line from "The Gallic War."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.22,0:13:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't seem like a suicide to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have proof, but my experience \N as a cop tells me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Mr. Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?  This doesn't look good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If his death wasn't a suicide, that means \N your life may be in danger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He... he was my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute... I already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither his background nor his birthplace \N has anything to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Fahren was a good person, not \N the type who could deceive people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.70,0:14:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he did try to deceive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The master needs his rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have to ask you to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not finished with this investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not because you are paying me a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.06,0:14:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something more sinister lurking behind everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In life...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In life, there are some things that cannot be undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children's Bill of Rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's something like an international agreement...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to protect the rights of children who are in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working on this topic right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Volunteering to take care of these children at \N the orphanage has nothing to do with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just something I enjoy doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, tell us the rest of what you were talking about earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three times that Schuwald filed for bankruptcy, and...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, during those three times, he suddenly disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:16:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he reappeared, it was as though \N he had been totally rejuvenated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said something about that during  \N one of our Friday reading sessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ask him where he went during \N those times when he disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's take him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has a place where they can go to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, it's looking at the homes from \N the rooftop of the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kunz...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The drain in the bathroom seems to be clogged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take a look at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sink over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lotte, what is wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, open up!  Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, open up!  Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you taking Mr. Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes are bad, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!  This is kidnapping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!  Everything went according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere nice, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you are not Margot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.91,0:17:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need some information on the late Mr. Fahren.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to see you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fahren?  Which one are you referring to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were two different groups...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with men claiming to be Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with blond hair, or the one with black?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with black hair came with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine, that a girl would actually \N follow him to such a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy with black hair and a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.83,0:18:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...actually claimed to be Schuwald's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be right... It should be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you taken me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbenberg Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this place would help cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The colors of the autumn leaves are beautiful, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, very beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the wrens?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear the wrens singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is just a construction site now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful chorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Many apples have fallen from the trees onto the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come take a look over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a spectacular sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rays of the setting sun shining \N through the autumn leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their radiance reflecting off the serene lake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it too, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:21:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe such a beautiful place actually exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.49,0:21:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.76,0:21:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said two different groups came, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The young man with black hair came with a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Fahren didn't come alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, someone else came with the blond guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Fahren guy you are asking about hardly said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was his friend that did all the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which one it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd believe him if he said he was Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the other guy?
